    "body": "A long time ago I set out to make this part of the mandatory representation of tags in rust (including the bit-packing on unused pointer bits). I'd be willing to revive the concept, though I'll admit it feels weird to encode as a first-class language feature, and likely hard to cover all cases.\n",
