    "created_at": "2012-06-01T23:37:22Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-06-01T23:37:22Z",
    "body": "Agreed, building in option is more complex than is warranted.  To address @pcwalton's objection, just have an annotation for specifying the layout of an enum from the various choices we have available.  In the absence of such an annotation, we just select as we think best.\n",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
